description:
Older brother of Inumura Hinaginu, and heir to their family business of doll making.
He is already dead but came back to life thanks to his guardian cat Noro. He is sprouting an evil eye on his forehead, that has been bestowed onto him by said cat spirit. With that he can see spirits and even make them disappear.
He is the holder of the Etiquette bead.
name: Inumura Daikaku
